  },
  "transliteration": "Wa‘adakumullāhu magānima kaṡīratan ta'khużūnahā fa‘ajjala lakum hāżihī wa kaffa aidiyan-nāsi ‘ankum, wa litakūna āyatal lil-mu'minīna wa yahdiyakum ṣirāṭam mustaqīmā(n)."
